# L10 Automating with Approvals

<index>

- Defining Approval Processes
- Options for Approving Records

### Approval Processes

single or muilti-step processes that require end -user authorization for record promotion

- Initial Submission Actions
- Step Definition
- Final Actions
- Final Approval Actions
- Recall Actions

### comparison

| workflow and Process Builder | Approval Processes |
| --- | --- |
| record save | clicks â€œsubmit for Approvalâ€ or autosubmitted by a Process or a Flow |
| supports multiple criteria nodes that each have a set of actions | criteria(entry, step), actions(step, initial, rejection and approval) |

